ause a stir: One vice-chancellor has suggested causing a stir to bring about change, indicating dissatisfaction with the current system and emphasizing the need for effective quality assurance that addresses emerging trends in higher education. This call for change highlights concerns about the potential impact of the proposed single quality assessment body on institutional autonomy, regulation, accountability for public funding, and the maintenance of high standards in Welsh universities.">
